Author: chris12312
Text: Also random, but does other people's weight gain bother you too? Some of my friends and family gained weight and it bothers me for some reason. But at the same time when my family loses weight it also really bothers me too. Little triggers go off in my head like "oh you lost 5lbs well guess what I'll lose 10lbs by the time I see you next. Suck it bitch!" I really hate the way my brain works.
